document_data.name: Palace of the Chief Examiner
document_data.mainbody: The '''Palace of the Chief Examiner''' was the headquarters for the city guard of [[Dhaztanar]] in [[Semphar]] during the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Location: The palace was located within the [[Furdah Rustauk District]] in southwest Dhaztanar. The Palace of the Chief Examiner was actually constructed along the shore of [[Gbor Nor]] at the base of the Caliph's Pier.
